the rest of the story,

09:04.159 --> 09:06.089
uh, follow me in the pool room,
please.

09:10.833 --> 09:13.067
Go ahead, Paul.
You know you want to.

09:16.889 --> 09:18.639
I think you're
rushing into this.

09:18.674 --> 09:20.808
