categorically not true!

10:02.101 --> 10:03.334
Yes, it is.

10:03.352 --> 10:06.036
So what?

10:06.038 --> 10:07.571
Is it not better

10:07.573 --> 10:09.690
that I settle and I have someone

10:09.691 --> 10:10.958
