and end up an old maid?

10:13.228 --> 10:15.863
Honey, that smells
of desperation.

10:15.897 --> 10:18.366
You don't... you
don't need that.

10:18.400 --> 10:21.835
You deserve the
greatest guy in the world.

10:21.870 --> 10:25.173
Oh, God. Oh, God.
I don't believe I'm about to say this.

10:25.207 --> 10:26.574
Sit down, sit down.

10:26.608 --> 10:32.680
Listen, I've been doing a...
doing a lot of thinking recently

10:32.714 --> 10:38.519
